dev.galactic.star.database.impl.mapping.annotations

Annotation Type DatabaseField


  • @Target(value=FIELD)
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface DatabaseField
    Declares whether the field is a parameter.
    Author:
    Verox001
